c: 14
v: 6
t: "Nabiyow ku marah Nabii Muusâ xaagu cus, isi marak : yi maraw Yallih niqmatay sin amol yani kassita, firqawnaa kee kay maray uma digaala sin tammoysay lab xaylo siinik yasguudeeh say xaylo siinik xixxibaane luk nuwwuk cabak sin naggoyse waqdi, too balay sin geytee kee siinit abe naggoysiyyat sin Rabbik kaxxa mokkoro siinik edde tan keenik iyye"